    "It also provides approximately 21% better results than POA and approximately 9% better results than POS for non-sensitive data.",
    "Figure 4 shows a graphical representation of Table 2.Table 3 presents the block creation times of the PoW, PoS, and PoA mechanisms.",
    "According to these results, the PoS mechanism with non-sensitive data provides the highest results.",
    "It is followed by the PoA mechanism with sensitive data, the PoW mechanism with sensitive data, the PoA mechanism with non-sensitive data, and the PoW mechanism with non-sensitive data, respectively.",
